<p>
<c:forEach items="${photoBoard.files}" var="photoFile">
<img src='${pageContext.servletContext.contextPath}/upload/photoboard/${photoFile.filepath}' height='80'>
</c:forEach>
</p>

사진: <input name='photoFiles' type='file'><br>
